column5: GCD that is some crazy fishing video. What pound test? LOL My question was once they hooked them how did they fall of the hook so easy?  Man your arms would be tired. Also makes you wonder how we have any Tuna left?  Part One is Good to watch.    Thanks Nemo
I prefer my tuna with lots of cheese.....melting runny cheese:
Thanks GCD that boat is unbelievable.  Definitely overkill.
Very cool vid! Fishing has come a long way since then!
